{"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"bindProperty","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"kind":"genericParameter","text":"ObjectT"},{"kind":"text","text":">("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"sourceProperty"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UnsafePointer","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gchar","text":"gchar","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":">!, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"target"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ObjectT"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"targetProperty","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SP","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafePointer"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"gchar","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gchar"},{"text":">!, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"flags"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"BindingFlags","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12BindingFlagsV","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingFlags","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject10BindingRefV","text":"BindingRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"! ","kind":"text"},{"text":"where","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ObjectT"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ObjectProtocol","text":"ObjectProtocol","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject0B8ProtocolP"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Whenever the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"sourceProperty"},{"text":" is changed the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"targetProperty"},{"type":"text","text":" is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"updated using the same value. For instance:"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["  g_object_bind_property (action, \"active\", widget, \"sensitive\", 0);"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"C"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Will result in the “sensitive” property of the widget "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" instance to be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"updated with the same value of the “active” property of the action "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"instance."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"flags"},{"type":"text","text":" contains "},{"code":"bidirectional","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" then the binding will be mutual:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"if "},{"code":"targetProperty","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" on "},{"code":"target","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" changes then the ","type":"text"},{"code":"sourceProperty","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" on ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"will be updated as well.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The binding will automatically be removed when either the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source"},{"text":" or the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"target"},{"type":"text","text":" instances are finalized. To remove the binding without affecting the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"source","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and the "},{"code":"target","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" you can just call ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_unref()"},{"type":"text","text":" on the returned"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Binding","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" instance."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Removing the binding by calling ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_unref()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" on it must only be done if"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the binding, "},{"code":"source","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"target","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" are only used from a single thread and it","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is clear that both "},{"code":"source","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"target"},{"type":"text","text":" outlive the binding. Especially it"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is not safe to rely on this if the binding, ","type":"text"},{"code":"source","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"target"},{"text":" can be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"finalized from different threads. Keep another reference to the binding and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"use "},{"code":"g_binding_unbind()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instead to be on the safe side."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object"},{"text":" can have multiple bindings.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"bindProperty(sourceProp